title: Arena, Oooh Er, Missus! The Frankie Howerd Story [BBC Four] [Xvi
description:
Arena, Oooh Er, Missus! The Frankie Howerd Story

First shown 1990

BBC Four - 09 April 2008

Aspect Ratio: 4:3 Fullscreen 532 x 400

Video: Xvid 900 kbps

Audio: MP3 128 kbps CBR Stereo

Showing as part of the Curse of Comedy season.
The life and career of Frankie Howerd, with help from friends and colleagues, including Max Bygraves, Vera Roper, Johnny Speight, Eric Sykes, June Whitfield and Michael Winner. With highlights from his television and film career.
